Apply targeted edits to a Pipeline Builder using Pipeline Builder DSL code.

 Provide a list of edits, each with searchValue (text to find) and replacement (replacement text).
 Each searchValue must have exactly 1 occurrence in the existing code.

 General guidelines:
 - Use PB.inputs.dataset(rid) to reference input datasets
 - Use PB.transforms.applyExpression() to apply expressions to transform data
 - Use PB.expressions.<expression_name> for column expressions
 - Use PB.literals for literal values (string, boolean, integer, etc.)
 - Use PB.outputs.dataset() to create output datasets with schemas
